cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.CR 

The paper deals with object tracking, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The techniques used in the paper involve machine learning algorithms such as One-Class SVM and Learning Based Digital Matting, which fall under the subcategories of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also evaluates its techniques on a tracking benchmark dataset, which falls under the subcategory of multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the paper deals with the problem of missing labels, which is a common problem in computer vision and can be addressed using techniques from the subfield of computer graphics (cs.CR).
